Requirements:-

common system to centralize bus booking.

system-
    -Type 1 users
    -Type 2 users

Type 1:-
    -admins
    -can modify vehicle details, cancel payments and route updates.
Type 2:-
    -users
    -can book tickets and cancel tickets.
    -inquire bus informations.




bus admins --------------------   system    --------------users 

system --------------bus DB
      |--------------user DB



